metadata.description:
SHARBI is a meme 2.0 cryptocurrency & NFT project that is owned by & developed by its decentralized community. 

SHARBI is the high-class mistress of SHIB 

Our art features world famous digital artists such as Archan Nair & SimonaArtOnline and other artists from the community.

We provide daily income to all holders via USDC but we are much more than this.  We are a community building alot of utility, helping to improve DeFi and spreading love.
